<i>Outer Party Member 984213...</i>

01:01:42.766 --> 01:01:45.326
<i>Devereux, Minitrue, Records Section.</i>

01:01:46.870 --> 01:01:49.338
<i>Outer Party member 9106...</i>

01:01:49.439 --> 01:01:51.930
<i>Dawes, Minitrue, Porno Section.</i>

01:01:53.009 --> 01:01:56.035
<i>Outer Party Member 38091...</i>

01:01:56.146 --> 01:01:58.512
<i>Ware, Minitrue, Porno Section.</i>

01:01:59.649 --> 01:02:02.675
<i>Outer Party Member 1 1792...</i>

01:02:02.786 --> 01:02:05.414
<i>Bigland, Minitrue, News Section.</i>

01:02:07.257 --> 01:02:11.455
"Items one, comma, five, comma, seven,
approved fullwise. Stop."

01:02:12.328 --> 01:02:16.731
"Suggestion contained item six doubleplus
ridiculous verging crimethink..."

01:02:16.833 --> 01:02:18.994
"Cancel, stop. End message."

