<i>Outer Party Member 4392...</i>

01:02:26.009 --> 01:02:29.501
<i>Rosenblum, Miniprod,
Light Industry Section.</i>

01:02:31.214 --> 01:02:34.411
<i>Outer Party Member 66755...</i>

01:02:34.517 --> 01:02:37.008
<i>Davis, Miniprod, Women's Section.</i>

01:02:40.323 --> 01:02:43.451
<i>That concludes the list
of known agents of Goldstein...</i>

01:02:43.560 --> 01:02:46.324
<i>actively engaged in the latest conspiracy....</i>

01:02:46.429 --> 01:02:49.762
Not much of this gets
to the Outer Party, I'm afraid.

01:02:51.701 --> 01:02:52.725
To our leader.

01:02:52.836 --> 01:02:56.772
<i>...that our eternal allies in Eurasia
are turning against us.</i>

01:02:58.441 --> 01:03:02.207
<i>More nests of conspirators
and saboteurs have been uncovered...</i>

01:03:02.312 --> 01:03:05.076
<i>and further arrests are expected shortly.</i>

01:03:12.722 --> 01:03:13.711
<i>You can....</i>

01:03:14.724 --> 01:03:17.784
Yes. We are allowed that privilege.

01:03:19.496 --> 01:03:21.088
Some more of this?

01:03:21.698 --> 01:03:23.290
It's called wine.

01:03:36.579 --> 01:03:41.414
There are thoughtcriminals
who maintain the Resistance is not real.

01:03:42.752 --> 01:03:44.583
Believe me, Winston...

01:03:45.288 --> 01:03:46.812
it is very real.

01:03:48.925 --> 01:03:51.758
Perhaps you are not familiar
with how it operates.

01:03:51.861 --> 01:03:54.193
I'm attentive to the news.

01:03:55.265 --> 01:03:56.391
Indeed.

01:03:56.733 --> 01:04:00.066
Perhaps you imagine
a huge network of conspirators...

01:04:00.169 --> 01:04:02.899
prepared to commit
any atrocity to demoralize...

01:04:03.006 --> 01:04:05.440
and weaken the order of our society.

01:04:05.975 --> 01:04:08.569
The reality is infinitely more subtle.

01:04:10.713 --> 01:04:12.578
If Goldstein himself...

01:04:13.216 --> 01:04:18.119
fell into the hands of the Thought Police,
he could not give them a list of his agents.

01:04:18.755 --> 01:04:20.780
Such a list does not exist.

01:04:22.559 --> 01:04:25.722
They're not an organization
in the sense we know.

01:04:27.196 --> 01:04:29.426
Nothing holds it together but an idea.

01:04:30.934 --> 01:04:34.165
There is no possibility of change
in their lifetime.

01:04:34.804 --> 01:04:36.965
In the face of the Thought Police...

01:04:37.240 --> 01:04:39.231
they cannot act collectively.

01:04:40.410 --> 01:04:42.901
Individually, they cheat...

01:04:43.846 --> 01:04:46.576
forge, blackmail, corrupt children...

01:04:46.683 --> 01:04:48.981
spread disease and prostitution...

01:04:51.354 --> 01:04:55.484
in the name of spreading knowledge
from generation to generation.

01:04:55.792 --> 01:04:56.952
Until...

01:04:58.628 --> 01:05:00.459
<i>in a thousand years....</i>

01:05:08.004 --> 01:05:10.598
You may find this of interest.

01:05:16.846 --> 01:05:18.143
Thank you.

01:05:28.958 --> 01:05:32.724
<i>...address a rally in Victory Square
at 21:30 hours.</i>

01:05:33.630 --> 01:05:36.121
<i>That is the end of the announcement.</i>

01:05:39.602 --> 01:05:41.194
Goodbye, brother.

01:05:52.148 --> 01:05:55.811
<i>They have attacked an unarmed village
with rocket bombs...</i>

01:05:55.918 --> 01:05:59.854
<i>and murdered 4,000 defenseless, innocent...</i>

01:05:59.956 --> 01:06:02.857
<i>and peaceful citizens of Oceania.</i>

01:06:04.994 --> 01:06:06.859
<i>This is no longer war.</i>

01:06:06.963 --> 01:06:09.158
<i>This is cold-blooded murder.</i>

01:06:11.401 --> 01:06:14.837
<i>Until now, the war has been conducted
with honor...</i>

01:06:15.204 --> 01:06:16.466
<i>and bravery...</i>

01:06:16.572 --> 01:06:21.066
<i>with the ideals of truth and justice,
in the best traditions of mankind...</i>

01:06:21.678 --> 01:06:23.805
<i>until this moment.</i>

01:06:26.249 --> 01:06:28.114
<i>Brothers and sisters...</i>

01:06:28.651 --> 01:06:32.018
<i>the endless catalogue of bestial atrocities...</i>

01:06:32.121 --> 01:06:34.954
<i>which will inevitably ensue
from this appalling act...</i>

01:06:35.058 --> 01:06:38.494
<i>must, can, and will be terminated.</i>

01:06:43.399 --> 01:06:45.560
<i>The forces of darkness
and treasonable maggots...</i>

01:06:45.668 --> 01:06:48.831
<i>who collaborate with them,
must, can, and will...</i>

01:06:49.138 --> 01:06:51.868
<i>be wiped from the face of the earth.</i>

01:06:52.508 --> 01:06:54.066
<i>We must crush them.</i>

01:06:54.177 --> 01:06:56.145
<i>We must smash them.</i>

01:06:56.245 --> 01:06:58.076
<i>We must stamp them out.</i>

01:06:59.582 --> 01:07:02.608
<i>We, the people of Oceania...</i>

01:07:06.923 --> 01:07:10.984
<i>...will not rest until a final victory
has been achieved.</i>

01:07:12.161 --> 01:07:16.222
<i>Death to the eternal enemy of Oceania.</i>

01:07:17.500 --> 01:07:18.467
<i>Death!</i>

01:07:26.209 --> 01:07:28.040
<i>Brothers and sisters...</i>

01:07:28.578 --> 01:07:30.910
<i>one week from now...</i>

01:07:31.814 --> 01:07:33.645
<i>in this very square...</i>

01:07:34.517 --> 01:07:37.816
<i>we shall,
as a demonstration of our resolve...</i>

01:07:38.688 --> 01:07:41.657
<i>as a sure sign to those
who attempt to threaten...</i>

01:07:41.758 --> 01:07:43.726
<i>our Party and our State...</i>

01:07:44.160 --> 01:07:46.788
<i>we shall execute publicly...</i>

01:07:46.896 --> 01:07:50.161
<i>the same number of Eastasian prisoners...</i>

01:07:50.266 --> 01:07:53.793
<i>by hanging, drawing and quartering.</i>

01:07:57.640 --> 01:07:59.835
<i>Big, Big, Big....</i>

01:08:45.121 --> 01:08:48.283
<i>"In accordance to the principles
of Doublethink..."</i>

01:08:48.424 --> 01:08:51.051
<i>"it does not matter if the war is not real..."</i>

01:08:51.160 --> 01:08:54.129
<i>"or when it is, that victory is not possible."</i>

01:08:54.462 --> 01:08:58.763
<i>"The war is not meant to be won.
It is meant to be continuous."</i>

01:08:59.702 --> 01:09:02.170
<i>"The essential act of modern warfare..."</i>

01:09:02.270 --> 01:09:05.399
<i>"is the destruction of the produce
of human labor."</i>

01:09:06.509 --> 01:09:11.139
<i>"A hierarchical society is only possible
on the basis of poverty and ignorance."</i>

01:09:13.049 --> 01:09:15.643
"In principle,
the war effort is always planned..."

01:09:15.751 --> 01:09:18.652
"to keep society on the brink of starvation."

01:09:19.455 --> 01:09:23.755
<i>"The war is waged by the ruling group
against its own subjects."</i>

01:09:23.859 --> 01:09:27.956
<i>"And its object is not victory
over Eurasia or Eastasia..."</i>

01:09:29.198 --> 01:09:32.689
<i>"but to keep the very structure
of society intact."</i>

01:09:38.374 --> 01:09:39.500
Julia?

01:09:40.776 --> 01:09:42.243
Are you awake?

01:10:01.998 --> 01:10:04.592
There is truth, and there is untruth.

01:10:06.702 --> 01:10:09.762
To be in a minority of one
doesn't make you mad.

01:10:14.744 --> 01:10:16.336
Julia, my love...

01:10:18.381 --> 01:10:19.939
I understand how.

01:10:21.884 --> 01:10:23.749
<i>I don't understand why.</i>

01:10:47.643 --> 01:10:48.974
I'm hungry.

01:10:51.213 --> 01:10:53.306
Let's make some more coffee.

01:11:11.334 --> 01:11:12.494
The water's cold.

01:11:21.777 --> 01:11:23.540
There's no oil in it.

01:11:25.181 --> 01:11:27.741
That's strange. I thought it was full.

01:11:31.454 --> 01:11:36.357
<i>They say that time heals all things</i>

01:11:38.160 --> 01:11:43.097
<i>They say you can always forget</i>

01:11:45.401 --> 01:11:49.337
<i>But the smiles and the tears</i>

01:11:49.572 --> 01:11:53.235
<i>across the years</i>

01:11:54.243 --> 01:11:58.771
<i>they twist my heartstrings yet.</i>

01:11:58.881 --> 01:12:00.405
She's beautiful.

01:12:06.389 --> 01:12:09.324
She's a meter across the hips. Easily.

01:12:09.992 --> 01:12:11.926
It's her style of beauty.

01:12:17.299 --> 01:12:18.994
The future is hers.

01:12:27.510 --> 01:12:29.034
We are the dead.

01:12:31.247 --> 01:12:32.771
We are the dead.

01:12:33.816 --> 01:12:35.408
<i>You are the dead.</i>

01:12:37.853 --> 01:12:40.014
<i>Remain exactly where you are.</i>

01:12:40.322 --> 01:12:42.756
<i>Make no move until you are ordered.</i>

01:12:48.030 --> 01:12:49.554
Now they can see us.

01:12:49.665 --> 01:12:51.394
<i>Now we can see you.</i>

01:12:51.700 --> 01:12:53.668
<i>Clasp your hands behind your heads.</i>

01:12:55.171 --> 01:12:58.663
<i>Stand out in the middle of the room.
Stand back-to-back.</i>

01:12:59.375 --> 01:13:01.343
<i>Do not touch one another.</i>

01:13:04.313 --> 01:13:05.940
The house is surrounded.

01:13:06.048 --> 01:13:07.948
<i>The house is surrounded.</i>

01:13:09.618 --> 01:13:11.813
I suppose we may as well say goodbye.

01:13:11.921 --> 01:13:15.152
<i>You may as well say goodbye.
While we're on the subject...</i>

01:13:15.257 --> 01:13:18.021
<i>"Here comes a candle to light you to bed."</i>

01:13:18.461 --> 01:13:21.225
<i>"Here comes a chopper
to chop off your head."</i>

01:14:34.937 --> 01:14:36.370
Pick that up.

01:14:52.188 --> 01:14:53.621
Thought Police.

01:15:32.394 --> 01:15:35.454
<i>6079 Smith. Open your eyes.</i>

01:16:01.790 --> 01:16:03.087
Parsons.

01:16:05.694 --> 01:16:07.628
Keep away from me, Smith.

01:16:09.698 --> 01:16:11.666
I'm an agent of Goldstein.

01:16:17.239 --> 01:16:19.173
I didn't know it myself.

01:16:21.644 --> 01:16:24.511
Thoughtcrime is so insidious.

01:16:26.482 --> 01:16:28.450
It just creeps up on you.

01:16:36.325 --> 01:16:38.293
My daughter found it out.

01:16:40.029 --> 01:16:41.656
Very proud of her.

01:16:43.899 --> 01:16:47.630
Very grateful I've been discovered
before it's too late.

01:16:53.742 --> 01:16:56.267
They won't shoot me, will they, Smith?

01:16:57.379 --> 01:17:00.405
I know I could be very useful
in a labor camp.

01:17:09.591 --> 01:17:11.286
<i>Room 101.</i>

01:17:19.068 --> 01:17:20.035
No.

01:17:21.570 --> 01:17:25.097
<i>Please, you don't have to take me there.</i>

01:17:26.642 --> 01:17:27.609
Why?

01:17:28.377 --> 01:17:30.675
There's nothing I won't confess.

01:17:31.780 --> 01:17:32.940
Nothing.

01:17:34.350 --> 01:17:36.477
I've told you everything already.

01:17:38.087 --> 01:17:40.351
What is it you want me to know?

01:17:43.425 --> 01:17:45.290
Take him instead of me.

01:17:45.828 --> 01:17:48.695
He's the thoughtcriminal. It's him you want.

01:18:40.749 --> 01:18:42.376
They got you, too.

01:18:43.152 --> 01:18:45.245
They got me a long time ago.

01:18:48.791 --> 01:18:51.282
You knew this would happen, Winston.

01:18:51.393 --> 01:18:54.419
Don't deceive yourself.
You've always known it.

01:19:12.080 --> 01:19:16.210
The photos of you and the girl
will be recycled for proletarian use.

01:19:55.791 --> 01:19:58.259
Do you know where you are, Winston?

01:20:00.629 --> 01:20:02.028
I don't know.

01:20:03.298 --> 01:20:04.663
I can guess.

01:20:06.101 --> 01:20:08.035
In the Ministry of Love.

01:20:09.037 --> 01:20:11.631
Do you know how long you've been here?

01:20:12.207 --> 01:20:13.231
No.

01:20:14.643 --> 01:20:15.769
Weeks?

01:20:16.979 --> 01:20:18.139
Months?

01:20:19.348 --> 01:20:21.714
Do you know why you're here?

01:20:25.220 --> 01:20:27.984
Shall I tell you why we brought you here?

01:20:28.790 --> 01:20:30.155
To cure you.

01:20:30.826 --> 01:20:32.418
To make you sane.

01:20:44.206 --> 01:20:45.503
That was 40.

01:20:45.607 --> 01:20:49.065
You can see that the numbers
on this dial run up to 100.

01:20:50.312 --> 01:20:53.213
Will you please remember
that, during our conversation?

01:20:53.315 --> 01:20:56.978
I have it in my power
to inflict pain on you at any time...

01:20:57.085 --> 01:20:59.451
and in whatever degree I choose.

01:21:06.128 --> 01:21:09.894
You know perfectly well
what is the matter with you, Winston.

01:21:10.098 --> 01:21:14.194
You've known it for years, though
you've fought against the knowledge.

01:21:14.303 --> 01:21:16.294
You are mentally deranged.

01:21:17.005 --> 01:21:19.439
You suffer from a defective memory.

01:21:20.909 --> 01:21:24.276
You never tried to cure yourself of it,
because you did not choose to.

01:21:24.713 --> 01:21:28.649
It was a small effort of will,
which you were not ready to make.

01:21:30.719 --> 01:21:32.186
For example...

01:21:33.322 --> 01:21:36.052
which power is Oceania at war with?

01:21:37.926 --> 01:21:39.325
Eastasia.

01:21:41.496 --> 01:21:43.896
Oceania is at war with Eastasia.

01:21:45.067 --> 01:21:46.295
Eastasia.

01:21:47.069 --> 01:21:48.161
Good.

01:21:48.770 --> 01:21:52.501
And Oceania has always been at war
with Eastasia, has it not?

01:21:55.177 --> 01:21:57.907
Tell me what you think you remember.

01:22:03.085 --> 01:22:04.712
I remember...

01:22:06.655 --> 01:22:09.681
that until only a week
before I was arrested...

01:22:10.525 --> 01:22:13.153
we weren't at war with Eastasia at all.

01:22:14.963 --> 01:22:16.453
It was Eurasia.

01:22:19.001 --> 01:22:21.162
That lasted four years, I think.

01:22:21.269 --> 01:22:22.793
Another example.

01:22:23.438 --> 01:22:25.030
A serious delusion.

01:22:26.942 --> 01:22:30.207
Photographs about which
you've had hallucinations...

01:22:31.146 --> 01:22:33.910
which you believed you held in your hand.

01:22:36.251 --> 01:22:37.946
They never existed.

01:22:46.561 --> 01:22:48.893
Say what you were about to say, Winston.

01:22:48.997 --> 01:22:50.430
They exist...

01:22:52.067 --> 01:22:53.364
in memory.

01:22:55.404 --> 01:22:56.769
I remember.

01:22:58.373 --> 01:22:59.806
You remember.

01:23:01.209 --> 01:23:02.870
I do not remember.

01:23:04.179 --> 01:23:07.706
Only the disciplined mind
can see reality, Winston.

01:23:09.818 --> 01:23:12.286
It needs an act of self-destruction...

01:23:12.587 --> 01:23:14.077
an effort of the will.

01:23:15.323 --> 01:23:17.655
Do you remember writing in your diary:

01:23:17.759 --> 01:23:21.752
<i>"Freedom is the freedom to say
two plus two equals four"?</i>

01:23:23.932 --> 01:23:24.956
Yes.

01:23:25.400 --> 01:23:27.766
How many fingers am I holding up?

01:23:28.370 --> 01:23:29.394
Four.

01:23:29.871 --> 01:23:34.399
And if the Party says there are not four,
but five, then how many?

01:23:35.677 --> 01:23:36.735
Five.

01:23:43.985 --> 01:23:45.009
No.

01:23:46.521 --> 01:23:49.012
That's no use. You're lying.

01:23:50.692 --> 01:23:52.887
How many fingers, please?

01:23:56.765 --> 01:23:58.995
Four. What else could I say?

01:24:01.670 --> 01:24:04.969
Five, or anything you like.
Will you please stop it?

01:24:06.608 --> 01:24:08.098
Stop the pain.

01:24:12.514 --> 01:24:14.175
How can I help it?

01:24:17.252 --> 01:24:20.415
How can I help
what I see in front of my eyes?

01:24:22.390 --> 01:24:24.324
Two and two makes four.

01:24:25.527 --> 01:24:27.222
Sometimes, Winston.

01:24:27.996 --> 01:24:31.397
Sometimes they are five,
sometimes they are three.

01:24:32.567 --> 01:24:35.195
Sometimes they are all of them at once.

01:24:44.746 --> 01:24:48.739
Neither the past, nor the present,
nor the future...

01:24:49.351 --> 01:24:51.319
exists in its own right.

01:24:52.187 --> 01:24:54.348
Reality is in the human mind...

01:24:55.590 --> 01:24:57.785
not in the individual mind...

01:24:58.527 --> 01:25:01.860
which makes mistakes and soon perishes...

01:25:03.565 --> 01:25:05.829
but in the mind of the Party...

01:25:06.501 --> 01:25:09.800
which is collective and immortal.

01:25:13.675 --> 01:25:15.540
-Again.
-No.

01:25:23.418 --> 01:25:25.409
How many fingers, Winston?

01:25:27.722 --> 01:25:28.814
Four.

01:25:30.258 --> 01:25:32.522
Four, I suppose there are four.

01:25:33.461 --> 01:25:35.258
I tried to see five.

01:25:37.032 --> 01:25:38.590
I wish I could.

01:25:38.700 --> 01:25:39.962
Which do you wish?

01:25:40.068 --> 01:25:43.765
To persuade me that you can see five,
or really to see them?

01:25:44.306 --> 01:25:46.001
Really to see them.

01:25:48.710 --> 01:25:49.802
Again.

01:25:58.887 --> 01:26:00.479
How many, Winston?

01:26:12.334 --> 01:26:13.767
I don't know.

01:26:18.740 --> 01:26:19.900
Better.

01:26:38.093 --> 01:26:41.859
<i>No one escapes, Winston.
There are no martyrs here.</i>

01:26:43.265 --> 01:26:45.927
<i>All the confessions made here are true.</i>

01:26:47.435 --> 01:26:50.734
We do not destroy the heretic
because he resists us.

01:26:51.740 --> 01:26:54.766
As long as he resists us,
we never destroy him.

01:26:55.810 --> 01:26:58.870
We make him one of ourselves
before we kill him.

01:26:59.781 --> 01:27:02.875
We make his brain perfect
before we blow it out.

01:27:04.085 --> 01:27:05.416
And then...

01:27:06.521 --> 01:27:10.514
when there is nothing left
but sorrow and love of Big Brother...

01:27:11.426 --> 01:27:14.054
we shall lift you clean out of history.

01:27:14.696 --> 01:27:18.496
We shall turn you into gas
and pour you into the stratosphere.

01:27:19.434 --> 01:27:21.402
Nothing will remain of you.

01:27:22.037 --> 01:27:23.971
Not a name in a register.

01:27:24.673 --> 01:27:26.971
Not a memory in a living brain.

01:27:28.209 --> 01:27:31.975
You will be annihilated in the past,
as well as in the future.

01:27:34.349 --> 01:27:35.543
Three thousand.

01:27:43.992 --> 01:27:46.051
<i>This time it won't hurt you.</i>

01:27:48.296 --> 01:27:51.060
Before we bring this session to an end...

01:27:51.700 --> 01:27:54.168
I want you to ask me your questions.

01:27:54.502 --> 01:27:56.697
I want you to clear your mind.

01:28:00.241 --> 01:28:01.333
Julia.

01:28:02.243 --> 01:28:04.177
She betrayed you, Winston...

01:28:04.279 --> 01:28:06.577
immediately, unreservedly.

01:28:07.849 --> 01:28:12.183
All her rebellion, deceit,
folly, dirty-mindedness...

01:28:12.287 --> 01:28:14.312
has been turned out of her.

01:28:17.926 --> 01:28:19.826
Does Big Brother exist?

01:28:20.795 --> 01:28:22.092
Of course.

01:28:24.699 --> 01:28:26.428
The same way as me?

01:28:28.470 --> 01:28:30.062
You do not exist.

01:28:33.942 --> 01:28:38.140
You've not asked me the question
that is uppermost in your mind.

01:28:39.214 --> 01:28:41.375
You know what is in Room 101.

01:28:43.118 --> 01:28:45.518
Everyone knows what's in Room 101.

01:28:50.258 --> 01:28:51.384
Now...

01:28:52.527 --> 01:28:54.358
fix your eyes on mine.

01:29:11.579 --> 01:29:14.309
<i>What country is Oceania at war with?</i>

01:29:17.986 --> 01:29:19.578
<i>I don't remember.</i>

01:29:20.388 --> 01:29:22.879
<i>Oceania is at war with Eastasia.</i>

01:29:23.591 --> 01:29:25.388
<i>Do you remember that now?</i>

01:29:25.493 --> 01:29:26.585
Yes.

01:29:28.463 --> 01:29:30.829
<i>How many fingers am I holding up?</i>

01:29:32.834 --> 01:29:33.858
Five.

01:29:34.836 --> 01:29:37.930
You see, at least, that it is possible.

01:29:42.310 --> 01:29:45.245
You've understood the reality of the past...

01:29:45.680 --> 01:29:47.341
and of the present.

01:29:48.983 --> 01:29:50.712
Now for the future.

01:29:52.887 --> 01:29:54.479
A question:

01:29:55.323 --> 01:29:58.224
"How does one man
assert power over another?"

01:30:00.595 --> 01:30:02.392
By making him suffer.

01:30:02.697 --> 01:30:05.723
Exactly. Obedience is not enough.

01:30:07.635 --> 01:30:11.731
Power is inflicting pain and humiliation.
Otherwise, you cannot be sure.

01:30:12.173 --> 01:30:15.108
Power is tearing human minds apart...

01:30:16.511 --> 01:30:20.607
and putting them together again
in new shapes of your own choosing.

01:30:21.182 --> 01:30:23.650
Power is not a means, it is an end.

01:30:24.619 --> 01:30:28.988
In our world, there will only be triumph
and self-abasement.

01:30:30.158 --> 01:30:32.524
Everything else, we shall destroy.

01:30:33.228 --> 01:30:35.662
The past is forbidden. Why?

01:30:37.165 --> 01:30:40.293
Because when we can cut man
from his own past...

01:30:40.768 --> 01:30:45.205
then we can cut him from his family,
his children, other men.

01:30:47.909 --> 01:30:50.969
There is no loyalty,
except loyalty to the Party.

01:30:52.580 --> 01:30:55.515
There is no love, except love of Big Brother.

01:30:56.084 --> 01:30:59.986
All competing pleasures, we will destroy.

01:31:02.423 --> 01:31:05.790
If you want a vision of the future, imagine...

01:31:05.927 --> 01:31:08.657
a boot stamping on a human face forever.

01:31:16.738 --> 01:31:19.764
You are thinking
that my face is old and tired...

01:31:21.209 --> 01:31:23.370
that while I talk of power...

01:31:23.511 --> 01:31:26.571
I'm unable to prevent
the decay of my own body.

01:31:28.550 --> 01:31:30.984
But the individual is only a cell.

01:31:32.287 --> 01:31:36.053
And the weariness of the cell
is the vigor of the organism.

01:31:36.591 --> 01:31:38.991
-You'll fail.
-Why?

01:31:40.762 --> 01:31:42.320
It's impossible.

01:31:43.765 --> 01:31:47.394
Hatred, the fear of life.

01:31:48.169 --> 01:31:50.569
Why is hate less vital than love?

01:31:51.573 --> 01:31:53.040
I don't know.

01:31:53.208 --> 01:31:55.142
But somehow you'll fail.

01:31:56.044 --> 01:31:58.012
Something will defeat you.

01:31:59.480 --> 01:32:01.380
Life will defeat you.

01:32:01.816 --> 01:32:04.649
We control life at all levels.

01:32:06.054 --> 01:32:07.954
We create human nature.

01:32:09.023 --> 01:32:11.184
Men are infinitely malleable.

01:32:12.727 --> 01:32:17.323
Or perhaps you've returned to your old idea
that the proletarians will arise.

01:32:17.932 --> 01:32:19.866
Put it out of your mind.

01:32:20.401 --> 01:32:22.426
They are helpless animals.

01:32:23.271 --> 01:32:25.398
Humanity is the body.

01:32:26.975 --> 01:32:30.775
I don't care. In the end, they'll beat you.

01:32:31.913 --> 01:32:34.973
Sooner or later, they'll tear you to pieces.

01:32:36.884 --> 01:32:38.476
On what evidence?

01:32:40.188 --> 01:32:41.849
Goldstein's book.

01:32:43.224 --> 01:32:47.183
I wrote it.
Or, at least, I collaborated in writing it.

01:32:48.096 --> 01:32:51.031
No book is individually produced,
as you know.

01:32:52.634 --> 01:32:54.602
I just believe it.

01:32:56.738 --> 01:32:58.467
I know you'll fail.

01:33:00.141 --> 01:33:02.132
Something in this world...

01:33:03.144 --> 01:33:06.045
<i>some spirit you will never overcome....</i>

01:33:06.914 --> 01:33:08.973
What is it, this principle?

01:33:10.285 --> 01:33:11.912
I don't know.

01:33:13.288 --> 01:33:14.915
The spirit of man.

01:33:16.224 --> 01:33:18.488
And do you consider yourself a man?

01:33:19.294 --> 01:33:20.318
Yes.

01:33:23.131 --> 01:33:25.759
If you are a man, you're the last man.

01:33:27.201 --> 01:33:28.964
Your kind is extinct.

01:33:29.804 --> 01:33:31.601
We are the inheritors.

01:33:33.474 --> 01:33:36.068
Do you understand that you are alone?

01:33:37.879 --> 01:33:39.813
You are outside history.

01:33:41.182 --> 01:33:42.581
You unexist.

01:33:46.621 --> 01:33:47.781
Get up.

01:34:06.441 --> 01:34:07.738
Come here.

01:34:25.660 --> 01:34:27.025
Look at you.

01:34:28.496 --> 01:34:30.259
You're rotting away.

01:34:43.077 --> 01:34:44.806
That is the last man.

01:34:46.247 --> 01:34:49.080
If you are human, that is humanity.

01:34:51.052 --> 01:34:53.020
It will not last forever.

01:34:54.422 --> 01:34:57.289
You can escape from it
whenever you choose.

01:34:58.226 --> 01:35:00.057
Everything depends on you.

01:35:00.161 --> 01:35:01.526
You did it.

01:35:02.764 --> 01:35:05.130
You reduced me to this.

01:35:05.633 --> 01:35:07.032
No, Winston.

01:35:08.236 --> 01:35:10.295
You reduced yourself to it.

01:35:11.672 --> 01:35:13.537
When will you shoot me?

01:35:16.210 --> 01:35:18.075
Might take a long time.

01:35:19.347 --> 01:35:21.281
But don't give up hope.

01:35:22.083 --> 01:35:24.483
Everyone is cured sooner or later.

01:35:26.821 --> 01:35:28.413
And in the end...

01:35:29.957 --> 01:35:31.652
we shall shoot you.

01:35:32.527 --> 01:35:34.757
The law of gravity is nonsense.

01:35:35.730 --> 01:35:37.425
No such law exists.

01:35:38.099 --> 01:35:39.896
If I think I float...

01:35:40.601 --> 01:35:42.569
and you think I float...

01:35:43.070 --> 01:35:44.628
then it happens.

01:35:44.906 --> 01:35:46.237
I love you.

01:35:46.507 --> 01:35:49.999
You have the strength, Winston.
You have the whole Party.

01:35:50.545 --> 01:35:52.172
You are the Party.

01:35:52.513 --> 01:35:55.380
You're one of us, one of the chosen.

01:35:56.117 --> 01:35:57.482
I love you.

01:35:58.419 --> 01:36:00.011
I love you, too.

01:36:08.996 --> 01:36:10.258
Julia, my love.

01:36:21.943 --> 01:36:23.069
<i>Get up.</i>

01:36:29.784 --> 01:36:31.547
<i>Stand up straighter.</i>

01:36:32.987 --> 01:36:34.750
<i>Look me in the face.</i>

01:36:39.060 --> 01:36:42.962
Tell me, Winston, and remember, no lies.

01:36:45.099 --> 01:36:48.227
What are your true feelings
towards Big Brother?

01:36:49.504 --> 01:36:51.938
-I hate him.
-You must love him.

01:36:53.541 --> 01:36:55.634
It's not enough to obey him.

01:36:56.477 --> 01:36:58.104
You must love him.

01:37:00.281 --> 01:37:01.543
Room 101.

01:37:29.043 --> 01:37:32.206
You asked me once, Winston,
what was in Room 101.

01:37:33.314 --> 01:37:37.045
I told you that you knew, already.
Everyone knows.

01:37:40.388 --> 01:37:42.686
The thing that is in Room 101 ...

01:37:43.891 --> 01:37:46.189
is the worst thing in the world.

01:37:57.438 --> 01:37:59.998
It goes beyond fear of pain or death.

01:38:01.509 --> 01:38:05.309
It is unendurable,
and it varies from individual to individual.

01:38:06.814 --> 01:38:10.580
It may be burial alive or castration...

01:38:11.552 --> 01:38:13.486
or many other things.

01:38:18.225 --> 01:38:20.716
In your case, it is rats.

01:38:21.896 --> 01:38:22.920
No.

01:38:28.402 --> 01:38:30.836
Please. What do you want me to do?

01:38:31.205 --> 01:38:33.537
You will do what is required of you.

01:38:33.841 --> 01:38:36.309
What? What is it?

01:38:37.445 --> 01:38:40.312
<i>How can I do it if I don't know what it is?</i>

01:38:42.249 --> 01:38:45.377
In the proletarian areas,
they will attack a baby...

01:38:46.153 --> 01:38:49.088
and within five minutes, strip it to the bone.

01:38:49.857 --> 01:38:52.587
They also attack the sick and dying.

01:38:54.061 --> 01:38:58.691
They show astonishing intelligence
in knowing when a human being is helpless.

01:39:07.141 --> 01:39:08.802
Please.

01:39:13.748 --> 01:39:17.047
<i>The mask fits over your head,
leaving no exit.</i>

01:39:18.352 --> 01:39:19.979
<i>I press the first lever...</i>

01:39:20.087 --> 01:39:22.578
and the rats move into
the front compartment.

01:39:23.824 --> 01:39:27.453
I press the second,
and the door of the cage will slide up.

01:39:28.829 --> 01:39:32.196
These starving brutes
will shoot at you like bullets.

01:39:32.667 --> 01:39:35.659
Have you ever seen a rat
leap through the air?

01:39:39.440 --> 01:39:42.967
They will leap onto your face
and bore straight into it.

01:39:43.811 --> 01:39:46.405
Sometimes they attack the eyes first.

01:39:48.783 --> 01:39:52.617
Sometimes they burrow through the cheeks
and devour the tongue.

01:39:57.658 --> 01:40:01.389
Tell me. What do you want?

01:40:07.301 --> 01:40:08.666
No, please.

01:40:16.811 --> 01:40:18.403
I love you.

01:40:20.448 --> 01:40:23.508
Do it to her! Do it to Julia!

01:40:23.984 --> 01:40:26.452
I don't care what you do to her,
but do it to her!

01:40:26.554 --> 01:40:29.580
Tear her my face off!
Do it to Julia, not to me!

01:40:31.225 --> 01:40:33.216
Do it to Julia!

01:40:37.131 --> 01:40:38.359
Not me!

01:40:42.837 --> 01:40:46.773
<i>A vast military buildup has been reported
in the Sahara Desert...</i>

01:40:46.874 --> 01:40:49.308
<i>in Sectors 17 and 18 of the war zones.</i>

01:40:50.678 --> 01:40:53.169
<i>That is the end of the announcement.</i>

01:41:32.453 --> 01:41:33.647
Brother.

01:41:42.563 --> 01:41:43.996
On the house.

01:41:51.806 --> 01:41:53.569
Thank you for coming.

01:41:57.611 --> 01:42:01.672
<i>You are warned to stand by
for an important announcement at 15:30.</i>

01:42:02.149 --> 01:42:04.617
<i>This is news of
the gravest national consequence...</i>

01:42:04.718 --> 01:42:06.652
<i>concerning the war with Eurasia.</i>

01:42:06.754 --> 01:42:07.914
<i>15:30.</i>

01:42:09.857 --> 01:42:12.519
Are you worried about the African front?

01:42:14.695 --> 01:42:19.223
<i>The news is disquieting in the extreme.
I've been worrying about it all day.</i>

01:42:20.067 --> 01:42:22.558
It's not just a question of losing Africa.

01:42:22.670 --> 01:42:27.369
For the first time, the territory of Oceania
itself is threatened by invasion.

01:42:27.608 --> 01:42:29.269
<i>It's inconceivable.</i>

01:42:37.251 --> 01:42:40.516
It must have been possible
to outflank them in some way.

01:42:47.962 --> 01:42:49.623
I have an instinct.

01:42:51.498 --> 01:42:53.125
There's bad news on the way.

01:42:59.006 --> 01:43:00.997
I told them all about you.

01:43:04.378 --> 01:43:07.677
I'm only thankful they got me
before it was too late.

01:43:08.082 --> 01:43:10.380
Yes, I told them about you, too.

01:43:11.452 --> 01:43:12.942
Thoughtcrime...

01:43:15.422 --> 01:43:17.390
sexcrime, all your treachery.

01:43:26.367 --> 01:43:28.358
I have a meeting to go to.

01:43:32.373 --> 01:43:33.897
We must meet again.

01:43:36.710 --> 01:43:37.768
Yes.

01:43:40.848 --> 01:43:42.577
We must meet again.

01:44:00.267 --> 01:44:02.963
<i>I accuse myself of the following crimes:</i>

01:44:04.004 --> 01:44:06.802
<i>I have seduced Party members
of both sexes...</i>

01:44:07.374 --> 01:44:09.934
<i>I've been to the proletarian areas...</i>

01:44:10.377 --> 01:44:13.972
<i>I deliberately contracted syphilis
in order to spread the disease...</i>

01:44:14.081 --> 01:44:16.549
<i>to my wife and other Party members.</i>

01:44:17.184 --> 01:44:20.950
<i>Together with other agents,
I have counterfeited banknotes...</i>

01:44:21.789 --> 01:44:26.158
<i>wrecked industrial machinery,
polluted the water supply...</i>

01:44:27.061 --> 01:44:29.996
<i>guided Eurasian rocket bombs
to targets on Airstrip One...</i>

01:44:30.097 --> 01:44:32.429
<i>by means of coded radio signals.</i>

01:44:34.368 --> 01:44:38.168
<i>I stand here, a victim of the influence
of Emmanuel Goldstein.</i>

01:44:39.073 --> 01:44:40.938
<i>Guilty on all counts.</i>

01:44:42.743 --> 01:44:45.837
<i>I'm glad I was caught.
I was mentally deranged.</i>

01:44:47.247 --> 01:44:48.714
<i>Now I am cured.</i>

01:44:50.351 --> 01:44:54.788
<i>I ask only for you to accept
my love of our leader.</i>

01:44:56.223 --> 01:45:00.421
<i>I ask only to be shot
while my mind is still clean.</i>

01:45:12.973 --> 01:45:14.668
<i>A glorious victory!</i>

01:45:14.908 --> 01:45:17.433
<i>A vast, strategic maneuver to outflank...</i>

01:45:17.544 --> 01:45:21.310
<i>the Eurasian Forces on the African front
has been successful.</i>

01:45:22.383 --> 01:45:27.320
<i>Perfectly coordinated, it has resulted
in the utter rout of the Eurasian Army.</i>

01:45:28.222 --> 01:45:33.023
<i>There have been nearly a million prisoners.
It has been an utter rout.</i>

01:45:33.994 --> 01:45:35.188
Waiter?

01:45:37.631 --> 01:45:42.091
<i>This immense victory brings the war
within measurable distance of its end.</i>

01:45:44.138 --> 01:45:45.628
Wonderful news.

01:46:43.297 --> 01:46:44.594
<i>I love you.</i>

